-- Club Med board to meet on Bonomi bid -source
-- By Dominique Vidalon
-- Tue Jul 01, 2014 10:32AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, July 1 (Reuters) - Club Mediterranee's <CMIP.PA> board of directors will meet on Tuesday to review an offer made by top shareholder Andrea Bonomi for the French resort operator, a source close to the matter said.

"The board will meet this afternoon and look at the terms of the offer," the source said, without providing further details.